-- Anarchist Group Claims Responsibility for Rome Parcel Bombs, Corriere Says
-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 2010-12-24T06:40:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-24/anarchist-group-claims-responsibility-for-rome-parcel-bombs-corriere-says.html
 An anarchist group claimed
responsibility for two bombs that exploded in Rome yesterday,
injuring two people, Corriere della Sera reported, without
saying where it got the information.  The group, Informal Anarchist Federation, left a message in
a box near the site of the second bombing at the Chilean
embassy, Corriere said. Police are seeking to authenicate the
message, the daily said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  